R Scripts for making components of Figure 2 of Dreos et al. (PLoS Comput Biol. 2021)

Input files:

Position probability matrices

   cons_dm6_K3_s1_1.mat
   cons_dm6_K3_s1_2.mat
   cons_dm6_K3_s1_3.mat
   cons_hg19_K3_s1_1.mat
   cons_hg19_K3_s1_2.mat
   cons_hg19_K3_s1_3.mat

Scripts: 

Unmodified scripts from seqLogo R package downloaded from
http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/src/contrib/seqLogo_1.54.3.tar.gz

   pwm.R
   seqLogo.R

Modified seqLogo2 function for Figure 2

   seqLogo2_fig2.R

Script to generate the sequence logos for Figure 2 in PDF fromat 

   fig2.R (Usage Rscript --vanilla fig2.R)

Output files:

Sequence logos

   fig2_dm6_class1_logo.pdf
   fig2_dm6_class2_logo.pdf
   fig2_dm6_class3_logo.pdf
   fig2_hg19_class1_logo.pdf
   fig2_hg19_class2_logo.pdf
   fig2_hg19_class3_logo.pdf
